  "description": "A panoramic view of a city situated next to a large body of water, captured during a vibrant sunset. The sun is low on the horizon, casting a warm golden glow across the water and reflecting off the buildings. The city appears densely populated with a grid-like street pattern. Hills and distant mountains form the backdrop, silhouetted against the colorful sky. The sky itself is a dramatic display of orange, yellow, and purple hues, with cloud formations adding texture and depth. Foreground trees provide a natural frame for the urban landscape. A distinct layer of haze hangs over the distant hills, softening the contrast between the land and sky.",
